{"tid":2452751,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"元朗中槍少年暴動罪成 還柙至4月7日判刑","createTime":"2021-03-19T04:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T09:02:41.000Z","uid":240362,"like":25,"dislike":331,"uniUserReply":118,"replies":[{"pid":"3f0d4ef1bb37b94bd8c3b87a1c9b81ac47f405e6","tid":2452751,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:39:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14509\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14509&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSrc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=7ba0892e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14509</a><br />\n<br />\n#粉嶺裁判法院第二庭  ( 少年庭 )<br />\n#蘇文隆主任裁判官<br />\n#答辯 #1004元朗<br />\n<br />\n*庭外消息*<br />\n<br />\n👤*(15)  <br />\n<br />\n控罪：有意圖導致他人身體受嚴重傷害，暴動<br />\n<br />\n手足認罪，現在還柙，等候教導所報告，押後至2021年4月7日 12:00，於粉嶺裁判法院第二庭判刑。"},{"pid":"20de02cbd877dbc8f8312dcfd3159863965f8085","tid":2452751,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57764c7c3ba2831a3cb99415398f838efc4a9b21","tid":2452751,"uid":184261,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:40:04.000Z","msg":"教導所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"717a82f30dedb503c8235bad685f9b65132ae71d","tid":2452751,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f01e723505a72d5e33ec725f51e35702feaf1c07","tid":2452751,"uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:41:33.000Z","msg":"控罪：<br />\n(1) 有意圖而導致他人身體受嚴重傷害<br />\n被告被控於10月4日元朗大棠路及青山公路元朗段交界與其他不知名人士意圖非法及惡意導致警員1877 陳港橋Chan Kong Kiu 身體受嚴重傷害<br />\n<br />\n(2) 暴動<br />\n被告被控於10月4日元朗大棠路及青山公路元朗段交界與其他不知名人士參與暴動<br />\n<br />\n被告承認控罪二，控方表示撤銷控罪一，存於法庭檔案內。法庭表示為被告索取教導所報告，期間被告需要還押‼️<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至4月7日1200於粉嶺裁判法院二號庭判刑。<br />\n（感謝臨時直播員報料💛）"},{"pid":"22358d8b4641222894d12f3d4b8e533ee0e008e2","tid":2452751,"uid":231480,"like":100,"dislike":3,"score":97,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:42:27.000Z","msg":"明明係件黑警開槍傷人，而家調轉"},{"pid":"6f4b606a44628c069816beb13f5e2cbe01f8640f","tid":2452751,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:43:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40188febb59dc854647dde30aff1cf09cef89143","tid":2452751,"uid":221171,"like":58,"dislike":2,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:44:13.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">國家殺人</span></span>"},{"pid":"39fa2b77879ae056f05ea567b5f9a619e8e14a29","tid":2452751,"uid":51271,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:44:15.000Z","msg":"比蘇狗判都應該好重手"},{"pid":"3f9df8b39c3a591137caa28b82fb99b0a5ec28fd","tid":2452751,"uid":214997,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:44:27.000Z","msg":"比真槍射再比人告返轉頭"},{"pid":"29ddd2c23da50f307e20543f2b917bdc8ebd0491","tid":2452751,"uid":66087,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:45:15.000Z","msg":"邊個仲信香港有未來真係傻豬豬"},{"pid":"0f5060539699ecc1f24c9244721ddd32fe03f01d","tid":2452751,"uid":221171,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kGPYSh3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkGPYSh3.jpg&h=d7f7642b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qMB05C4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqMB05C4.jpg&h=440f5e74&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27ca7fc28c7a6e483430467cc948108b4862b4ed","tid":2452751,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T